{"tid":1496721,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[824] 去觀塘既各位IT人又有野做啦","createTime":"2019-08-22T15:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T03:30:42.000Z","uid":42668,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7bc83e9a1a99c16bed71cedef6dec5f01e1ed214","tid":1496721,"uid":42668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:55:41.000Z","msg":"824觀塘遊行獲發不反對通知書 政府資科辦<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重申智慧燈柱不讀取身份證資料</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2433122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2433122&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=6e9e733f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2433122</a><br />\n<br />\n我地依家咩事都要fact check<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我地一齊fact check下佢個circuit究竟有幾多function啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去觀塘既巴絲記住幫手fact check下個燈柱circuit啊<br />\n最好唔好影埋相上黎,好多IT巴絲都識睇, 大粒既IC chip要清少少<br />\n<br />\n咩係IC chip:<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.smart-prototyping.com/image/cache/data/2_components/Chip/101789%20ESP32%20IC/1-750x750.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smart-prototyping.com%2Fimage%2Fcache%2Fdata%2F2_components%2FChip%2F101789%2520ESP32%2520IC%2F1-750x750.jpg&h=de724ea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有能力既記住唔好攞個cam走,<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>記住唔好影上黎</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住呢啲野要喺post title前面加返個&quot;[IT]&quot;或者&quot;[824]&quot; 先易搵"},{"pid":"e7f2ee27b1cd291a5a293248c2184dd1bd2a007a","tid":1496721,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:56:35.000Z","msg":"點拎"},{"pid":"ef864189d8790132fd135154c8ca30b4772d73f6","tid":1496721,"uid":42668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7f2ee27b1cd291a5a293248c2184dd1bd2a007a","tid":1496721,"uid":8